item.title: JSON, Tabular Data, & R Lists: Part 1
item.description: Inspiration I was recently asked if I could help out with a project that involved parsing out JSON (JavaScript Object Notation) data. I am really grateful that I become involved on this because I had no prior experience with JSON structured data but the knowledge I gained from some of the challenges I ran into has been priceless.
